'''锂镧锆氧化物'''（缩写：'''LLZO'''，化学式：Li<sub>7</sub>La<sub>3</sub>Zr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>12</sub>）是一种锂充填的[[石榴石|石榴石结构]]材料，目前正处于固态电解质的应用研究中。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Yeandel|first=Stephen R.|last2=Chapman|first2=Benjamin J.|last3=Slater|first3=Peter R.|last4=Goddard|first4=Pooja|date=2018-12-13|title=Structure and Lithium-Ion Dynamics in Fluoride-Doped Cubic Li7La3Zr2O12 (LLZO) Garnet for Li Solid-State Battery Applications|url=https://doi.org/10.1021/acs.jpcc.8b07704|journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry C|volume=122|issue=49|pages=27811–27819|doi=10.1021/acs.jpcc.8b07704|issn=1932-7447}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Tsai|first=Chih-Long|last2=Ma|first2=Qianli|last3=Dellen|first3=Christian|last4=Lobe|first4=Sandra|last5=Vondahlen|first5=Frank|last6=Windmüller|first6=Anna|last7=Grüner|first7=Daniel|last8=Zheng|first8=Hao|last9=Uhlenbruck|first9=Sven|last10=Finsterbusch|first10=Martin|last11=Tietz|first11=Frank|date=2018-12-18|title=A garnet structure-based all-solid-state Li battery without interface modification: resolving incompatibility issues on positive electrodes|url=https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2019/se/c8se00436f|journal=Sustainable Energy & Fuels|language=en|volume=3|issue=1|pages=280–291|doi=10.1039/C8SE00436F|issn=2398-4902|access-date=2020-12-12|archive-date=2022-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319190231/https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2019/SE/C8SE00436F|dead-url=no}}</ref>它具有高离子电导率，适于用作电解质。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Ramakumar|first=S.|last2=Deviannapoorani|first2=C.|last3=Dhivya|first3=L.|last4=Shankar|first4=Lakshmi S.|last5=Murugan|first5=Ramaswamy|date=2017-07-01|title=Lithium garnets: Synthesis, structure, Li+ conductivity, Li+ dynamics and applications|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0079642517300427|journal=Progress in Materials Science|language=en|volume=88|pages=325–411|doi=10.1016/j.pmatsci.2017.04.007|issn=0079-6425}}</ref>它可由[[碳酸锂|碳酸锂]]、[[氧化镧|氧化镧]]和[[二氧化锆|二氧化锆]]在高温反应制得：<ref name=Junji />
: 7 Li<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> + 3 La<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + 4 ZrO<sub>2</sub> → 2 Li<sub>7</sub>La<sub>3</sub>Zr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>12</sub> + 7 CO<sub>2</sub>↑

